<!-- README -->
<!-- Standard attribute definitionss -->
<!-- size: the number of bytes in the data if singular or in a single item if a collection or data (int) -->
<!-- num:  the number of items in the collection (only applies to collections) (int) -->
<!-- addy: the ROM offset of the data/collection of data (hex string) -->
<!-- pointer: an offset where a pointer to the addy is usually stored. useful for dealing with hacked roms (hex string) -->

